Package: smartremote
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-yaml
Description: Single-GPU remote job dispatcher with human-in-the-loop
 SmartRemote ingests Markdown job files (submitted over SFTP), runs each in an
 isolated workspace, serializes GPU work behind a lock, and bridges human
 decisions to WhatsApp/email via a Hermes Agent gateway so a job can park
 instead of block. The orchestrator is deliberately dumb; intelligence lives in
 pluggable runners (a cloud planner, a local executor).
 .
 This package installs the `smartremote` command-line dispatcher. The systemd
 unit and Hermes gateway are configured separately (see the documentation).
